PROG AQUA urs:1
KOPF DREI-STOECKIGER RAHMEN, QUERSCHNITTE AUS IY
NORM EN 199X-200X
MATE 1 30000 GAM 0
QB 1 MNR 1 B 1.0[m] H (12*0.00600000)**(1/3)[m]
QB 2 MNR 1 B 1.0[m] H (12*0.00466666)**(1/3)[m]
QB 3 MNR 1 B 1.0[m] H (12*0.00200000)**(1/3)[m]
ENDE

PROG SOFIMSHA urs:2
KOPF DREI-STOECKIGER RAHMEN
SYST RAHM
KNOT (1 4 1) (0 3)  0  FIX PXMZ ; KNOT 1 FIX F
STAB (1 3 1) (1 1) (2 1) QNR (1 1)
MASS (2 4 1) 200,200,100
ENDE

